      <div class="msgContentFrame">Just wondering what your experiences have been with this ability when fighting in a party against mobs much higher level than you. <br /> <br />I find that when soloing it hits so frequently, but when I fight much harder mobs I see the stamina bar go down but no animation and resist notification but the ability fails to either launch or affect the mob. <br /> <br />I suspect (as I see the stamina drain) that the mob is somehow resisting it, but without any animation or confirmation this is purely speculation.  Albeit a viable and possibly correct guess. <br /> <br />Do the rest of you experience this at all? <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 26th 2010  5:17am by MisterGaribaldi </span></i></div>
