      <div class="msgContentFrame">Okay, here is my observation with this... <br /> <br />If you hit comrade in arms too early, i.e: when you dont ALREADY have enough Stamina ... It will &quot;activate&quot;, but not place the debuff... but will drain your stamina when you DO have enough.. <br /> <br />It has hit (observationally speaking) 100% of the time when I already had enough stamina and TP... but I will say it hits 0% of the time when I hit the ability too early.... yet it will still activate the cooldown on the move, and will drain my Stam... <br /> <br />Support on this? I attributed it to a bug, not a &quot;miss&quot; or &quot;resist&quot;<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Maverik <br />Paradise Oblivion <br />75SMN/41WHM/45BRD/37RNG/75COR <br />Maverick Hawkeye. Kashuan.</div></div>
